e Reflexionen &middot; Europäische Religionsgeschichte &middot; Religion und Moderne &middot; Religion und Gewalt &middot; Religion und Recht.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 4aAufsatzsammlung. 4aBibliographie. 4aKippenberg, Hans Gerhard. 4aReligionsgeschichte. 4aReligionswissenschaft. 7aRELIGION / Religion & Science.2bisacsh  aKippenberg, Hans G.  aReligious History.  aReligious Science.1 aAuffarth, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBenavides, Gustavo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBosch, Lourens P. Van Den, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBremmer, Jan N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrunotte, Ulrike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBräunlein, Peter J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCancik, Hubert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEisenstadt, Shmuel N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFallers Sullivan, Winnifred, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrankfurter, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrese, Hans-Ludwig, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGladigow, Burkhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGraf, Fritz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHannemann, Tilman, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKohl, Karl-Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKuiper, Yme, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLawson, E. T